 we expect such a host galaxy sample to be\ncollected within a decade or two, prior to the advent of third-generation GW\ndetectors.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 10 May 2019 18:00:01 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 28 May 2019 15:03:27 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-06-12"}
