have low extinction and the rest are well fit by a \"Milky-Way-like\" extinction\nlaw. However, Collinder~220 hints at a possible \"LMC-like\" extinction law. We\nfinally provide a comprehensive point-source catalog to the community as a tool\nfor future investigation.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 10 May 2019 19:48:00 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-07-10"}
