ty of RHF+ph-AFQMC for simulating dense solids.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 10 May 2019 19:54:50 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 10 Jul 2019 00:56:39 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-08-20"}
